Debug stub: use service runtime interfaces for thread suspension

Work around circular deps between debug_stub and sel by specifying sel twice.

ATTENTION: this change temporarily removes the ability to set the registers on suspended threads on Windows (it never worked on platforms other than Windows). The feature will be back when supported in service_runtime.

